                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Under the Ruler of Death's guidance, the Lord of the Night created the Night Kingdom.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Night Kingdom",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the war of the Heavenly Principles and the dragons, Natlan's Ley Lines were severely damaged. To reconstruct them, Yohualtecuhtin reassembled the yet-intact components into a new structure and created the Night Kingdom, which stores all memories and souls of Natlan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7417,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Capitano",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Captain merged with the Lord of the Night to restore and change the Ley Lines in Natlan. Because of his immortality, the Night Kingdom can exist forever.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
